FEATURES OF JAVA
1:-SIMPLE
-Java is very easy to learn as its syntax is very simple.
-It's Syntax is based on C++.
-No complicated features like pointers,operator overloadoning etc.
-Automatic Garbage collection to remove unreferenced objects and thus programmers are free from memory management responsibilities.

2:-Object Oriented
-Java is object Oriented programming language.
-Just like the real world, it is centered on creating objects, manipulating objects and making them work together.
-Object oriented programming is better than procedural programming because it provides great flexibility,modularity ,clarity and reusabilty
-OOPs is more secure as it provides data hiding features.

3:-Platform Independent
-""Write oncez  
